Package antlr

Interface GramaticaListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
GramaticaBaseListener
public interface GramaticaListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by GramaticaParser.
